Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:03:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 代我向你在御手洗的父母問好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:11.54,tittle,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「等待漲潮的島上聽到的聲音」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很好嗎 如果不會太打擾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能見到好久不見的爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也邀請了小香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多久沒去御手洗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺跟爸爸有些像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然爺爺有時會來汐入玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我真的有很久沒去那座島上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海水的香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香碳 海風很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣悲戀的飛躍with香碳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是到哪裏都能飛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香跟乃理惠去過麻音家的旅館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪碳你太緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之放輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們也是第一次去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順利到達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就是御手洗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏還是大長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要再走一段路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎隱隱約約記得一些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香碳好厲害 會看地圖的小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒人看地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都好有禮貌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那邊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.34,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像來過這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼一說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音的…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 放輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真是太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等候多時了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音多虧你們照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是麻音的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們能跟麻音做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…真的太謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音…麻音是個非常溫柔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這事兒以後再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡…歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裝扮真適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 大家都進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然什麼都沒有 但是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之一樓是客室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是浪漫呢 香碳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天黑之前幹點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拍街道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要在旅館幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音 喝完茶之後帶大家參觀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能應付得來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那我去準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音在給家裏幫忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她要繼承這裏成為下一任的老闆娘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她的父母說做自己喜歡做的事也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 麻音是獨生女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏跟竹原很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼有種回家的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說嘴裏念著自己的願望鑽過這下面 願望就會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望暑假每天都能跟香碳見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 希望薰碳成為出色的魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺技 跟香碳的奇跡愛的飛躍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音就是在這裏長大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有魚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是香碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼魚呢 金槍魚？ 緣側魚？ 青花魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼每樣都是壽司材料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往天上飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要骨折了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我現在外出中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙女座？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榻榻米的氣味還很新
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近經過重修 變得漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有舞台誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好奇那裏對麻音有什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒能確定是個特別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想登上那個舞台之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能是旅館的老闆娘或只能是口笛師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夾在父母與夢想之間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 哪裏有鐘錶店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:10:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你是想說時間能解決一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐘錶店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐘錶店就在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐘錶店怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺說他今天會來拿要送去修理的表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這可真是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天能見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香碳的爺爺會來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這時候打過招呼了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚輩的名字是岡崎乃理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次的臭屁小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 拍一張留念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍照 拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奶奶家就在這島上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香 我們在這裏相遇是命運的安排呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒語 魔術 你用了什麼奇怪巫術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽過了 你是鑽過那個下面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂什麼喂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓 香 來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 麻棒 很久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓跟小香也長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然小時候有一起玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不記得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼澤渡先生 我還有貨要送
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下也會去麻棒家的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫小町
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直跟小香很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說誰一直跟你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱…咱是楓的祖…祖父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小啪的 爺爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰 乃理惠 麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音家就是長閒亭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 有跟楓同年的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 表呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦 雖然花了點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間鐘錶店會從世界各地收到修理的委託的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界各地？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是很有名的鐘錶店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這島也有大師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓從不同國家來的表在這島上好好運轉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又再送回世界各地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說我的甜點也有可能送到世界各地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得一來 大家來喝杯茶如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興 爺爺大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個早熟的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是名產的檸檬羊羹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 您知道長閒亭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長閒亭是我家 我為您帶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我要去為客人帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶你們到停車場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧 麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.53,0:14:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有點擔心 果然我們也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起 小香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶特製的牡丹餅準備好了 快回來 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 居然這種時候來 奶奶真不是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香抱歉啊 我必須要回家幫奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再跟你決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶的牡丹餅 yaho~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說 我累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你們搬行李
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我們自己來搬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這也是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由有招待之心的人招待客人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在努力地要招待好客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為麻棒是個努力的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 我差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話送上你們一程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這是奶奶的甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼暑假的時候爺爺去竹原玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,peace
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是peace
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:15:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海產啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚的天國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是龍宮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很新鮮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,康吉鰻飯還能再添哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃太多了 再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 大家吃得那麼乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 麻音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在幫忙洗碗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有空的話去起居室那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是想要麻音繼承旅館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 大家請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在麻音也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在高中有好好幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是個不太說話的孩子 有給大家添麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音 很努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個鄭重的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 還不能讓麻音嫁給…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該吐槽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直對自己說總有這麼一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 雖然不知是什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人果然想讓麻音繼承旅館嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音好像想從事音樂之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也好像很喜歡旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然想讓麻音做自己喜歡的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個　　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這間旅館也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是麻音碳今天也一直盯著乙女座的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那裏是重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候 我覺得我看到了很厲害的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在那上面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能使用將很多人的心連在一起那樣的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想著也許我也能做到也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.77,0:19:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那裏對我來說是重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這間旅館也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養育我長大的這間旅館也是我重要的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然將來的事自己也很模糊不清
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爸爸媽媽守護的這間旅館的工作 我也想幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能很好地跟客人交流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而添了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音想招待客人的心情都好好地傳遞給大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爺爺也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啤酒哥哥也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音的事我全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前就不擅長說話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音向著喜歡的道路前進就可以了 我們是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家擔心她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音真的交到了很好的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也許會遇到其它想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本這孩子小時候開始夢想就經常變的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 最初也阻止我們去起居室了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.13,0:21:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底那裏有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音碳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有隱瞞的事是不好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柱子上有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油性筆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子說過要成為漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又說要成為能進布偶裏面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是幾時的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學三年級的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說要成為魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要買大禮帽和魔術棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這孩子會從形式開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想變太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是自己選擇的路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為麻音自己想成為的東西就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 口笛師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.30,0:22:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 去找個好師傅收你為徒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上島的叔叔好像很擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸會這麼溫柔地看著孩子的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.14,0:22:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像能裝進軟綿綿的夢想一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的爸爸也是這樣看著守護我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.70,0:24:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有過想成為啦啦隊的人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.91,0:24:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 玉響~hitotose~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.76,0:24:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「千尋來了」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:23.52,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さい頃は　神樣がいて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:33.02,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不思議に夢をかなえてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:42.12,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優しい氣持ちで目覺めた朝は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:51.87,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人になっても　奇跡はおこるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:19:01.30,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,カーテンを開いて　靜かな木漏れ陽の
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:09.87,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やさしさに包まれたなら　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:20.25,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目にうつる全てのことは　メッセージ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:23.52,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候 有神靈存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:33.02,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議地為我實現了夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:42.12,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著溫柔的心情覺醒的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:51.87,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使變成大人 奇跡一樣會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:19:01.30,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉開窗簾 靜靜地從樹葉間漏下來的陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:09.87,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被溫柔包圍的話 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:20.25,in ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映在雙眼的一切 都傳達一種信息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:02.32,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}君が指で創るフレームには
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:08.86,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}蒲公英の綿毛が映りこむよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:15.13,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}格子窗 竹細工 急な階段
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.23,0:23:21.48,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}懷かしい景色もそのままだね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:28.11,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}そこにある何氣ないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:34.28,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}手のひらからこぼれてても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:41.34,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}恐れないで 止まらないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:47.74,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}君は君のままでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:54.67,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}神樣は時々惡戲する
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:24:07.52,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}一番大切なものだけを どこかに置き去りにさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:14.29,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}僕たちを大人にするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:21.60,ed jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}君を大人にするんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:02.32,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}在你手做的框架上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:08.86,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}映照著蒲公英的絨毛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:15.13,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}格子窗 竹工藝品 陡峭的樓梯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.23,0:23:21.48,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}令人懷念的景色還是如舊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:28.11,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}存在在那的無意之事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:34.28,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}即使從手心中溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:41.34,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}也請不要害怕 請不要止步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.86,0:23:47.74,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}請你如常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:54.67,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}神有時會惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:24:07.52,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}讓人把最重要的事物棄之不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:14.29,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}把我們變成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:21.60,ed cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(300,300)}把你變成大人
